{"tid":560290,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"2018年2月最新手機升級Android 8.0名單","createTime":"2018-02-14T03:12:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-14T03:14:56.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3c6eb929948f7bda2dd09fc71ac2905e008dac0f","tid":560290,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T03:12:42.000Z","msg":"展望2018年，仲有邊啲手機可以升上去 Android 8.0呢？以下整理2018年2月12日最新升級名單懶人包。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.kocpc.com.tw/archives/182858\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kocpc.com.tw%2Farchives%2F182858&d=nZ3leCUZjns4JbAcFq8YcC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=a00b2827\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.kocpc.com.tw/archives/182858</a>"},{"pid":"c8e527c8460188255db34053ca12c687aa3d181f","tid":560290,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T03:14:56.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://media.kocpc.com.tw/kocpc/2018/02/1518434507-6b93c2f7472fbce1615aa446f1e2ff4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.kocpc.com.tw%2Fkocpc%2F2018%2F02%2F1518434507-6b93c2f7472fbce1615aa446f1e2ff4e.jpg&h=c7fdfd97&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n1.HTC:<br />\n<br />\nA.升級名單:<br />\n<br />\nHTC 目前內建Android 8.0的手機為HTC U11+。由於HTC 近期手機都是基於Android 7.1深度定製的HTC Sense，所以不少新機必然會升級Android O（安卓8.0），甚至Android P（安卓9.0）。HTC 可以升級Android O的機型為HTC U11、 HTC U Ultra、HTC U Play、HTC Desire 10 Pro、HTC Desire 10 Lifestyle、HTC 10 Evo、HTC 10與HTC U11 EYEs都可望升級為Android 8.0。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://tel3c.tw/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/1518431456-985c998c0ced6773bade9699fb2e1b85.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftel3c.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2F1518431456-985c998c0ced6773bade9699fb2e1b85.jpg&h=a279a697&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n其中，HTC U11、HTC 10已經在去年11月釋出Android 8.0升級。根據版主所掌握非常可靠的最新消息，C/P超高的HTC U Ultra將會在今年二月底前釋出升級，讓U Ultra成為旺年開春首款升級Andoid 8.0的手機， U Ultra 用戶農曆年後就可以準備灑花了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nB.確定不會升級Android 8.0的名單:<br />\n<br />\nHTC Desire 728、 One E9s、Butterfly 3、A9、One M9、 One M9 Plus、 One M8、One M8s。"}]}